'use strict'
 
module.exports = function i18nChain () {
  var first = null
  var current
  for (var i = 0; i < arguments.length; i++) {
    var handler = arguments[i]
    if (handler) {
      var next = {
        handler: handler
      }
      if (!first) {
        first = next
      } else {
        current.next = next
      }
      current = next
    }
  }
  return {
    get: function (key) {
      var current = first
      while (current) {
        var value = current.handler.get(key)
        if (value !== null && value !== undefined) {
          return value
        }
        current = current.next
      }
    }
  }
}
